793
00:57:18,570 --> 00:57:19,670
and go home.

794
00:57:29,820 --> 00:57:30,920
So, Mom,

795
00:57:32,150 --> 00:57:34,820
please let it slide this once.

796
00:57:37,460 --> 00:57:38,690
Today will be...

797
00:57:39,590 --> 00:57:40,860
the last time.

798
00:57:46,170 --> 00:57:47,599
I remember that.

799
00:57:49,139 --> 00:57:51,940
The last moment when the patient
recognized people's faces.

800
00:57:53,269 --> 00:57:54,340
When was it?

801
00:58:01,349 --> 00:58:02,420
Min Ik.

802
00:58:06,289 --> 00:58:07,590
Veronica Park?

803
00:58:08,719 --> 00:58:09,719
Yes.

804
00:58:11,389 --> 00:58:12,389
But...

805
00:58:13,800 --> 00:58:14,829
where's the umbrella?

806
00:58:16,800 --> 00:58:17,869
I didn't bring it.

807
00:58:19,099 --> 00:58:20,800
I wasn't going to bring it
in the first place.

808
00:58:24,840 --> 00:58:28,409
Then why did you want to see me?

809
00:58:34,280 --> 00:58:37,289
Because I have an indigestion.

810
00:58:38,989 --> 00:58:39,989
What?

811
00:58:43,519 --> 00:58:45,030
When I think of you,

812
00:58:48,599 --> 00:58:49,659
I have a funny feeling...

813
00:58:52,500 --> 00:58:53,599
in my stomach.

814
00:58:58,070 --> 00:58:59,840
I guess I have an indigestion.

815
00:59:07,619 --> 00:59:09,980
The moment he met
someone he loved.

816
00:59:11,750 --> 00:59:14,590
He said he saw
the woman's face clearly.

817
00:59:21,730 --> 00:59:24,230
He saw it so vividly to a wonder.

818
00:59:43,050 --> 00:59:45,750
(The Secret Life of My Secretary)

819
00:59:46,289 --> 00:59:47,860
I don't know what's going on.

820
00:59:47,860 --> 00:59:49,159
Do you still trust people?

821
00:59:49,159 --> 00:59:50,360
Resign before
the stockholders meeting.

822
00:59:50,360 --> 00:59:52,690
I can't see
who is trying to support me.

823
00:59:52,690 --> 00:59:54,360
- Do Min Ik.
- If there's anyone who saw it,

824
00:59:54,360 --> 00:59:55,530
I will take care of them.

825
00:59:55,530 --> 00:59:56,860
Can I see you for a second today?

826
00:59:56,860 --> 00:59:58,570
Awesome! Bye!

827
00:59:58,570 --> 01:00:00,130
I'm pretty?

828
01:00:00,230 --> 01:00:01,340
I can see you.
